	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus diriget/dirigat corda Civitatum, quo nihil adprobent, quam quod consonum sit verbo domini puro.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varii sparguntur rumores de missa papist[ic]a invehenda in nostras Civitates.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt varię practicę a <placeName type="auto_name">Caesareanis</placeName>; verum dominus absque dubio dissipabit eas, si nos veram pęnitentiam egerimus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinę</placeName> agatur, in ista scheda inclusa invenies, dein quid in <placeName ref="l61" cert="high">Saxonia</placeName>; quas schedas cupio remitti cum tua oratione, quam habuisti contra Interim, et si quid praeterea habes, quod contra Interim ab aliis sit scriptum, oro, velis communicare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Senatus noster ea, quae propositurus est paganis, nobis praelegit; nos non potuimus ea comprobare.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De hac re alias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim, <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> 1548. 28. Novembris in ipso prandio.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Theodorum</persName>, <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">[Zving]lium</persName> nomine meo salutabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> vos omnes salutat in domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man sagt, der von <placeName type="auto_name">Rosenberg</placeName> und der von <placeName type="auto_name">Heideg</placeName> seyen in kaiserlicher ach, item der von <placeName type="auto_name">Büchlingen</placeName>, der graff sey <foreign xml:lang="la">deprehensus in adultero</foreign> und erschossen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der keyser soll hefftig kranck sin, das mann in müsse ätzen; <foreign xml:lang="la">nunquam ita periculose laboravit.</foreign></s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Id a quodam nobili <placeName type="auto_name">Ensesheimensi</placeName> audivi, qui ex Buxlla ad nos venit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Diser brieff gehört dem wolgelerten herren meyster Heinrich Bullinger, lütpriester zuͦ Zurich, mynem gunstigen herren zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zurich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
